title: Dietetic Internship Seminar
description: A forum for dietetic interns to make presentations and share their experiences in their supervised practice. Guest presentations on current issues in nutrition therapy, foodservice management and community nutrition. Total credit limited to 6 units, with a maximum of 2 units per quarter. Credit/No Credit grading only. 2 seminars.
prerequisites: Acceptance into the Cal Poly, San Luis Obispo Dietetic Internship, a special session program in Extended Education
